  "A couple invests $8,000 at 7% compounded monthly for their child's education. They plan to withdraw it in 15 years. What is the approximate total interest earned?": "一对夫妇每月投资8 000美元,每月7%,用于子女教育。他们计划在15年内收回这笔利息。所得利息总额约为多少?",
  "A = $8,000(1 + 0.07/12)^(180) ≈ $22,700. Interest earned = $22,700 - $8,000 = $14,700. Compound interest nearly tripled their original investment.": "A = 8 000(1美元+0.07/12) (180)  22 700美元,利息收入 = 22 700美元 - 8 000美元= 14 700美元,复合利息几乎是最初投资的三倍。",
